  <brief_title>Study of Safety and Efficacy of Letrozole Monotherapy as Second-line Endocrine Therapy in Postmenopausal Patients With Advanced Breast Cancer Who Received Previous Anti-estrogen Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Safety and Efficacy of Letrozole Monotherapy as Second-line Endocrine Therapy in Postmenopausal Patients With Advanced Breast Cancer Who Received Previous Anti-estrogen Treatment</official_title>
